{
  "text": "The same simulations were used to produce the plot of Fig. 3 by recording the trajectories of the process leading to a given fluctuation value [CITATION_1] , in this case A \u03c4 = 0.45 \u00b1 0.02 for the parameters listed in the caption of that figure. The padding \u00b10.02 is added to make sure that paths are actually selected in simulations; it does not influence their shape in any significant way.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "119115189"
